This is a satirical standup meeting note generator with a retro CRT terminal aesthetic. The humor and visual style are intentional and core to the project identity.

Tech stack: React 18, TypeScript (strict), Vite 5, Tailwind CSS 3, Lucide React for icons.

Design guidelines:
- Maintain the CRT/retro terminal aesthetic (scanlines, glitch effects, cyan-on-black color scheme)
- Keep the satirical corporate-humor tone in all generated content
- Use Tailwind CSS classes for styling; custom CSS only for animations in src/index.css
- Use functional React components with hooks only
- All code must pass TypeScript strict mode and ESLint checks

Do not install additional UI libraries, icon packs, or CSS frameworks unless explicitly requested. Use Lucide React for any new icons needed.
